1598
01:05:33,420 --> 01:05:35,059
- Okay.
- Please eat a little earlier...

1599
01:05:35,060 --> 01:05:36,689
- and meet me again at 2pm.
- Okay.

1600
01:05:36,690 --> 01:05:37,690
- See you.
- All right.

1601
01:05:38,590 --> 01:05:39,659
We'd better hurry.

1602
01:05:39,660 --> 01:05:40,660
(They must eat quickly.)

1603
01:05:40,960 --> 01:05:43,130
- Let's go, Ye Eun.
- Okay.

1604
01:05:43,330 --> 01:05:45,469
(The intern freshens up before going out for a meal.)

1605
01:05:45,470 --> 01:05:47,730
- Ye Eun!
- Yes.

1606
01:05:48,540 --> 01:05:49,600
Shin Ye Eun!

1607
01:05:49,700 --> 01:05:50,939
I'm coming.

1608
01:05:50,940 --> 01:05:52,209
