How did they contact you?

1617
01:06:11,060 --> 01:06:12,859
Did they call you and say,

1618
01:06:12,860 --> 01:06:13,890
"Hello, this is Team GBRB?"

1619
01:06:14,190 --> 01:06:16,159
They sent the proposal to my agency.

1620
01:06:16,160 --> 01:06:17,430
- I see.
- I see.

1621
01:06:17,860 --> 01:06:19,099
Do we have a proposal?

1622
01:06:19,100 --> 01:06:21,069
Yes, I even got photos of you.

1623
01:06:21,070 --> 01:06:22,099
Really?

1624
01:06:22,100 --> 01:06:24,810
The cast includes Doh Kyung Soo, Lee Kwang Soo.

1625
01:06:25,340 --> 01:06:27,509
I didn't know we had that.

1626
01:06:27,510 --> 01:06:30,710
(It's a company that has everything prepared.)

1627
01:06:31,110 --> 01:06:32,310
Ye Eun, do you like raw fish?

1628
01:06:32,510 --> 01:06:33,510
Yes.

1629
01:06:34,050 --> 01:06:35,150
We should get some, right?

1630
01:06:35,350 --> 01:06:36,350
(Nodding)

1631
01:06:36,450 --> 01:06:37,879
I need to make a reservation.

1632
01:06:37,880 --> 01:06:40,020
(A raw fish dinner is prepared to welcome the intern.)

1633
01:06:40,290 --> 01:06:42,659
Can you choose restaurants...

1634
01:06:42,660 --> 01:06:43,720
and make reservations yourself?

1635
01:06:43,820 --> 01:06:47,929
We're going to bet the meal cost with the production team.

1636
01:06:47,930 --> 01:06:50,730
(Planning a bet over the dinner bill with the production team)

1637
01:06:51,060 --> 01:06:52,630
That means...

1638
01:06:53,870 --> 01:06:55,870
you should also bring your wallet.

1639
01:06:56,070 --> 01:06:58,410
(Even the intern isn't exempt from paying the bill.)

1640
01:06:58,640 --> 01:07:00,110
It's raining harder than before.

1641
